-- BP Says Cost of Gulf Oil Spill Response Has Climbed to About $3.12 Billion
-- Will Kennedy
-- 2010-07-05T06:04:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/bp-says-cost-of-gulf-of-mexico-oil-spill-response-rises-to-3-12-billion.html

          
          
             BP Plc said the cost of responding to
the Gulf of Mexico oil spill had reached about $3.1 billion. It
expects an expanded oil containment system to start toward the
end of this week.  
          
          


  


        